        "exit_advice": "Exit OKLO. The discrete catalyst \u2014 Oklo signing a named data-center nuclear power supply deal \u2014 occurred December 18, two days before entry. The event is public, announced, and priced. No further concrete scheduled binary remains on this specific deal. The event-driven edge is gone."
